de.ityx.mediatrix.api.interfaces

Interface IBeanVariable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IVariable

    public interface IBeanVariable
extends IVariable
    IBeanVariable is a means of defining custom ActionCodes. Apart from being accessible in the class path IBeanVariables don't need to be installed - simple invocation performs class lookup and initialization.
